data.content: Caroline likely values the support system of friends and mentors more than just as a source of encouragement; this support may also play a significant role in her overall mental and emotional well-being. Caroline may feel a sense of urgency in her advocacy for inclusivity and understanding, possibly motivated by the current societal challenges faced by the LGBTQ community.
